=== 司法任命 ===
[[美国最高法院|美国最高法院]]在阿瑟任内两度出缺，首先是内战前就开始任职的民主党[[美國最高法院大法官|大法官]][[内森·克利福德|内森·克利福德]]1881年7月去世。阿瑟提名[[马萨诸塞州最高法院|马萨诸塞州最高法院]]知名法学家[[哈瑞斯·格雷|哈瑞斯·格雷]]，参议院以大幅优势确认。<ref name="Reeves1975" />{{rp|260–261}}<ref name="Howe1966" />{{rp|195}}格雷在最高法院一干就是20多年，直到1902年辞职<ref name="TLHall2001">{{cite book | last = Hall | first = Timothy L. | title = Supreme Court Justices: A Biographical Dictionary | url = https://archive.org/details/supremecourtjust00timo | pages = [https://archive.org/details/supremecourtjust00timo/page/186/mode/2up 186]–189 | publisher = Facts on File | location = New York, New York | year = 2001 | isbn = 978-0-8160-4194-7 | access-date = 2021-12-06}}</ref>。1882年1月大法官[[沃德·亨特|沃德·亨特]]退休，阿瑟提名昔日政坛领袖康克林，觉得有必要以高位报答知遇之恩，哪怕对方不大可能接受。事实也的确如此，康克林在参议院确认提名后谢绝，<ref name="Reeves1975" />{{rp|260–261}}<ref name="Howe1966" />{{rp|195}}这也是美国历史上最后一次总统提名的最高法院大法官人选在参议院确认后拒绝<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.senate.gov/legislative/nominations/SupremeCourtNominations1789present.htm | title = Supreme Court Nominations (1789-Present) | publisher = U.S. Senate | access-date = 2021-12-06 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211127141221/https://www.senate.gov/legislative/nominations/SupremeCourtNominations1789present.htm | archive-date = 2021-11-27 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。阿瑟接下来考虑参议员埃德蒙兹，但他谢绝提名机会<ref name="Doenecke1981" />{{rp|76}}；最终总统提名过去四年任[[美国联邦第二巡回上诉法院|第二巡回上诉法院]]法官的[[塞缪尔·布拉奇福德|塞缪尔·布拉奇福德]]，参议院在两周内确认<ref name="Reeves1975" />{{rp|260–261}}<ref name="Howe1966" />{{rp|195}}，布拉奇福德持续任职至1893年辞世<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.fjc.gov/history/judges/blatchford-samuel-m | title = Blatchford, Samuel M. | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210516063945/https://www.fjc.gov/history/judges/blatchford-samuel-m | dead-url = no | work = Biographical Directory of Federal Judges | publisher = Federal Judicial Center | access-date = 2021-12-06 | archive-date = 2021-05-16}}</ref>。

== 晚年（1885至1886年） ==
[[File:Chet_Arthur_Mad_Sq_jeh.JPG|thumb]]1898年立起乔治·埃德温·比塞尔创作的切斯特·艾伦·阿瑟雕像]]

阿瑟1885年离开白宫返回纽约故居，纽约州中坚派共和党人此前两个月纷纷要求他竞选联邦参议员，但他谢绝挽留，决定回归阿瑟、克奈瓦尔、勒森律师事务所<ref name="Reeves1975" />{{rp|412–414}}。他的工作情况受身体所限，只能满足助理律师工作需要，负责的案子很少而且经常因病情无法走出家门<ref name="Reeves1975" />{{rp|416–418}}。1885年结束前他在公众场合露面的次数屈指可数<ref name="Reeves1975" />{{rp|416–418}}。
[[File:Chester_Arthur_grave.jpg|thumb]]

阿瑟1886年夏在康涅狄格州避暑，回家后病重并在11月16日下令把不论公私所有文件焚毁{{refn|group="注"|留存的少量文件交由孙子加文保管，托马斯·里维斯20世纪70年代查阅并为阿瑟立传<ref>{{cite journal | title = The Search for the Chester Alan Arthur Papers | journal = The Wisconsin Magazine of History | first = Thomas C. | last = Reeves | volume = 55 | issue = 4 | date = Summer 1972 | jstor = 4634741 | pages = 310–319 }}</ref>。}}，次日早上他[[脑出血|脑出血]]发作后再也没有醒来。11月18日，切斯特·艾伦·阿瑟与世长辞，享年56岁。<ref name="Reeves1975" />{{rp|416–418}}葬礼22日在[[纽约天安教堂|纽约天安教堂]]举行，总统克利夫兰、前总统海斯等权贵出席<ref name="Reeves1975" />{{rp|418–419}}。阿瑟葬在奥尔巴尼县[[梅纳兹_(纽约州)|梅纳兹]][[奥尔巴尼乡村公墓|奥尔巴尼乡村公墓]]，与家人和先祖相伴{{refn|group="注"|阿瑟墓地标识的出生年份是1830<ref>{{cite news | dead-url = no | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211111214903/https://www.news10.com/news/president-chester-arthurs-birthday/ | url = https://www.news10.com/news/president-chester-arthurs-birthday/ | title = President Chester Arthur’s birthday | first = Jeff | last = Hunter | date = 2020-10-20 | work = WTEN | archive-date = 2021-11-11 | access-date = 2021-12-06}}</ref>，比实际晚一年，里维斯声称阿瑟出于虚荣把年纪报小。}}，石棺位于家族墓地角落，与夫人相邻<ref name="Reeves1975" />{{rp|416–418}}。1889年，纽约雕塑家[[以法莲·凯瑟|以法莲·凯瑟]]在阿瑟坟前竖立纪念碑，主体是上有青铜棕榈叶的花岗岩石棺，旁边屹立巨大的青铜天使雕像<ref>{{cite news | title = Monuments At Albany | newspaper = The New York Times | url = https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1894/01/07/104104464.pdf | date = 1894-01-07 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210831203248/https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1894/01/07/104104464.pdf | access-date = 2021-12-06 | archive-date = 2021-08-31 | dead-url = no | format = PDF}}</ref>。

阿瑟卸任总统后仅一年多便逝世，在历届美国总统中只比下台后三个月离世的詹姆斯·诺克斯·波尔克長<ref>{{cite web | last = Pinheiro | first = John | title = James K Polk: Life After the Presidency | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211126185300/https://millercenter.org/president/polk/life-after-the-presidency | dead-url = no | url = https://millercenter.org/president/polk/life-after-the-presidency | website = Miller Center | publisher = The University of Virginia | access-date = 2021-12-06 | date = 2016-10-04 | archive-date = 2021-11-26}}</ref>。

== 影响 ==
许多[[共和国大军|共和国大军]]哨所以阿瑟命名，如堪萨斯州[[尼馬哈縣_(堪薩斯州)|尼马哈县]][[戈夫_(堪萨斯州)|戈夫]]<ref>{{cite news | date = 1893-01-26 | title = Meeting of C. A. Arthur Post, No. 411 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211016122017/https://www.newspapers.com/image/481174683/ | dead-url = no | url = https://www.newspapers.com/image/481174683/ | work = The Goffs Advocate | location = Goff, KS | archive-date = 2021-10-16 | access-date = 2021-12-04 | via = Newspapers.com | page = 1}}</ref>、内布拉斯加州[[納科爾斯縣_(內布拉斯加州)|纳科尔斯县]][[劳伦斯_(内布拉斯加州)|劳伦斯]]<ref>{{cite news | date = 1891-08-30 | title = Leading Officials: The Three Principal Officers in the Nebraska Posts | url = https://www.newspapers.com/image/466338175/ | work = Omaha Daily Bee | location = Omaha, NE | via = Newspapers.com | access-date = 2021-12-06 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211016122014/https://www.newspapers.com/image/466338175/ | page = 13 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-10-16}}</ref>、俄勒冈州[[梅德福_(俄勒冈州)|梅德福]]<ref>{{cite news | date = 1892-09-23 | title = In the Encampment at the Reunion at Ashland | page = 3 | url = https://www.newspapers.com/image/94201757/ | work = Medford Mail | location = Medford, OR | via = Newspapers.com | access-date = 2021-12-06 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211016113318/https://www.newspapers.com/image/94201757/ | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-10-16}}</ref>、威斯康星州[[沃帕卡縣_(威斯康辛州)|沃帕卡县]][[奥格登斯堡_(威斯康辛州)|奥格登斯堡]]<ref>{{cite web | page = 12 | url = https://www.suvcw.org/garrecords/garposts/wi.pdf | title = Historical Summary of Grand Army of the Republic (GAR) Posts by State: Wisconsin | date = 2005 | author = National GAR Records Program | website = garrecords.org | publisher = Sons of Union Veterans of the Civil War | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211003080918/https://www.suvcw.org/garrecords/garposts/wi.pdf | dead-url = no | format = PDF | archive-date = 2021-10-03 | access-date = 2021-12-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | last = McCrory | first = Thomas J. | date = 2005 | title = Department of Wisconsin, Grand Army of the Republic | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=JeuBye82K0EC&pg=PA100&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | location = Black Earth, WI | publisher = Trails Books | isbn = 1-931599-28-9 | access-date = 2021-12-03}}</ref>。他1882年4月5日入选[[美国忠诚军团军事教团|美国忠诚军团军事教团]]哥伦比亚特区司令部<ref>{{cite book | last = Aubin | first = J. Harris | date = 1906 | title = Register of the Military Order of the Loyal Legion of the United States | url = https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_MoXlAAAAMAAJ | access-date = 2021-12-03 | page = [https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_MoXlAAAAMAAJ/page/n27/mode/2up 20] | location = Boston, MA | publisher = Military Order of the Loyal Legion of the United States, Commandery of Massachusetts}}</ref>，徽章号码02430<ref>{{cite web | url = https://rimollus.tripod.com/ | title = From the Headquarters Desk | last = Rhode Island Commandery | date = 2009 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211004045318/https://rimollus.tripod.com/ | website = Original Civil War Officer Members of MOLLUS | publisher = Military Order of the Loyal Legion of the United States | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-12-06 | archive-date = 2021-10-04}}</ref>，该荣誉可授予军官或平民，表彰他们对战事的显著贡献<ref>{{cite news | date = 1882-04-06 | title = The Loyal Legion: Meeting Last Night; President Arthur Elected to Membership | page = 1 | url = https://www.newspapers.com/image/68154593/ | work = National Republican | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211016152126/https://www.newspapers.com/image/68154593/ | location = Washington, DC | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2021-10-16 | access-date = 2021-12-06 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

阿瑟的母校联合学院1883年授予他法学博士[[名誉学位|名誉学位]]<ref>{{cite book | author = University of the State of New York | date = 1883 | title = Annual Report of the Board of Regents | location = Albany, NY | publisher = Weed, Parsons & Company | pages = 21–22 | access-date = 2021-12-03 | volume = 96 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=Rx0tAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA21&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr}}</ref>。

雕塑家[[乔治·埃德温·比塞尔|乔治·埃德温·比塞尔]]创作的阿瑟纪念雕像高4.6米，青铜人像矗立在花岗岩基座上，1898年在纽约[[麦迪逊广场|麦迪逊广场]]竖立，次年由阿瑟的九妹玛丽揭幕。战争部长[[羅脫|羅脫]]在仪式上称赞阿瑟是“充满睿智的政治家，管理工作坚定有效”，承认阿瑟在任上面临孤立，连所在政党都态度冷淡。<ref name="Reeves1975" />{{rp|419}}<ref>{{cite web | title = Chester A. Arthur | url = http://newyorkcitystatues.com/chester-a-arthur/ | publisher = New York City Statues | access-date = 2015-02-22 | dead-url = yes | archive-date = 2015-02-22 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20150222105814/http://newyorkcitystatues.com/chester-a-arthur/}}</ref>

阿瑟在现实生活中不受待见，历史学家的评价也是如此，离任后他几乎立刻消失在历史长河<ref name="Karabell2004" />{{rp|139}}。历史学家乔治·豪1935年表示，阿瑟在美国史上扮演重要角色，同时又奇怪地默默无闻<ref name="Howe1966" />{{rp|288}}。里维斯1975年指出，阿瑟任命的官员即使算不上杰出也异常可靠，那时的商界与政界充斥腐败和丑闻，但没有玷污他的政府<ref name="Reeves1975" />{{rp|420}}。[[扎卡里·卡拉贝尔|扎卡里·卡拉贝尔]]2004年为阿瑟立传，认为传主无论身体还是情绪上都有缺陷，但无疑竭尽所能为国效力<ref name="Karabell2004" />{{rp|139}}。正如豪在半个多世纪前总结的那样：“阿瑟的政治言行自成体系，遵守三大原则：对任何人言而有信、严防腐败、待人和蔼可亲的同时保持个人尊严。这些原则……令他与人们眼中传统的政治家截然不同。”<ref name="Howe1966" />{{rp|290}}

[[威廉·赫斯特|威廉·赫斯特]]买下阿瑟位于纽约的故居，现称[[切斯特·艾伦·阿瑟之家|切斯特·艾伦·阿瑟之家]]<ref>{{cite book | last = Hook | first = Eileen M. | date = 1986 | title = Hearst San Simeon State Historical Monument Visitor Center Interpretive Plan | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=F6A6AQAAIAAJ&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | access-date = 2021-12-06 | location = Sacramento, CA | publisher = California State Department of Parks and Recreation | page = 235 | via = [[Google圖書|Google Books]]}}</ref>，1944年起一直是卡鲁斯坦香料商场所在<ref>{{cite news | last = Roberts | first = Sam | date = 2014-12-07 | title = Where a President Took the Oath, Indifference May Become Official | access-date = 2021-12-06 | archive-date = 2021-11-20 | dead-url = no | location = New York, NY | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211120155333/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/08/nyregion/where-a-president-took-the-oath-indifference-may-become-official.html | work = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/08/nyregion/where-a-president-took-the-oath-indifference-may-become-official.html}}</ref>。

